                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:text="Unable to find your registration in the polls? Does your registration have your dead name, but your ID have your real name? Has your address changed?
\n\nThese are just some of the reasons to register to vote.
\n\nHere are the things you need to register:

\n\n• Complete a voter registration card online, in person, or print and mail it to the elections office.
\n• King County (Washington State) | Provide a copy of an approved ID:
\n• Driver’s license
\n• State ID card
\n• Student ID card
\n• Tribal ID card
\n• Employer ID card
\n• Outside King County | Provide a copy of an approved ID:
\n• Learn more at voteriders.org."
