                android:text="Instructions will accompany your Vote Early (Absentee) ballot. Follow instructions as noted, ensure you’re using the correct marking tool (e.g. pen or pencil).
\n\nRemember to sign your envelope as well.
\n\nIf you have further questions about how to complete your ballot and return it to your elections office, please call the following offices:
\n\n• In King County (Washington State) you can call (206) 296-VOTE.
\n• Outside King County you can call 1-866-OUR-VOTE."
                android:fontFamily="@font/rokkitt_regular"
                android:paddingRight="16dp"
                android:paddingLeft="16dp"
                android:layout_marginTop="8dp"
                android:gravity="center"
                app:layout_constraintEnd_toEndOf="parent"
